data.reasoningText:
`BinaryData.ToObjectFromJson<T>()` uses reflection-based JsonSerializer under the hood. I need to replace it with AOT-safe JSON parsing. Since we just need to get the "id" field from a JSON dictionary, I can use JsonDocument to parse it directly:

```csharp
using var doc = JsonDocument.Parse(ModelReaderWriter.Write(rehydrationToken, ModelReaderWriterOptions.Json, AzureResourceManagerContext.Default));
return doc.RootElement.GetProperty("id").GetString();
```

This is simpler and AOT-safe.

